  @{fg shine} Wallhall @{fg text}is a excellent (hehe) wall for /X, s!x and all compatibles.
             Check out the gr8 screenshots before installing!
       The things that makes this wall differ from other walls are:

                      » Up to @{fg shine}1ooo@{fg text} lines with tags! «
                       » Scrollable with cursors! «
                    » Can be used as "@{fg shine}G@{fg text}" command(!!) «
                    » Gr8 design by Magz & Grimlock! «

                           UNREGISTERED VERSION!

           TO RECEIVE A REGISTERED VERSION WITH YOUR BOARD NAME
                ON, JUST D!AL @{fg shine}GENETIC WASTE@{fg text} - +47-33o45192
                 AND UPLOAD A SMALL FILE AND ASK FOR ONE.

  
                            -magz of megastyle-

@endnode






